{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":378,"text":"I came here to show you"},{"time":2544,"text":"the Fotokite."},{"time":3829,"text":"It's a tethered, flying camera."},{"time":5931,"text":"But before I do that, I want to tell you a bit about"},{"time":8170,"text":"where it came from, what motivated it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":10344,"text":"So I was born in Russia,"},{"time":11839,"text":"and three years ago, in 2011,"},{"time":14948,"text":"there were the Russian federal elections."},{"time":17734,"text":"There were massive irregularities reported,"},{"time":19819,"text":"and people came out to protest,"},{"time":21476,"text":"which was very unlikely for Russia."},{"time":25170,"text":"And no one really knew"},{"time":26755,"text":"how significant these protests were,"},{"time":28839,"text":"because, for whatever reason,"},{"time":30253,"text":"the world media largely ignored it."},{"time":32237,"text":"Now, there was a group of photographers"},{"time":34319,"text":"who kind of flew flying cameras as a hobby —"},{"time":37637,"text":"usually photographing things like the Sphinx,"},{"time":40550,"text":"the Pyramids — who happened to be"},{"time":43318,"text":"right around the corner, and they flew a camera"},{"time":45973,"text":"and they took some snapshots,"},{"time":47749,"text":"some panoramas of this demonstration."},{"time":50326,"text":"Just completely independent entity,"},{"time":52159,"text":"completely random occurrence,"},{"time":54218,"text":"and the image, when I saw it, it really struck me."},{"time":57886,"text":"Here's one of the panoramas."},{"time":59460,"text":"So in a single image,"},{"time":60975,"text":"you can really see the scale of this event —"},{"time":64770,"text":"just the number of people,"},{"time":67838,"text":"the colors, the banners."},{"time":70525,"text":"You just can't consider this insignificant."},{"time":74366,"text":"All in a single image, which was really cool to me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":77368,"text":"And I think, in the future,"},{"time":79427,"text":"journalism and many other professions,"},{"time":81913,"text":"there are flying cameras already\nquite commonly out there,"},{"time":84432,"text":"but I think, you wait a few months, a few years,"},{"time":87873,"text":"and for many professions, it's really going to be"},{"time":89910,"text":"a requirement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":91755,"text":"And it make sense. It's \nsuch a unique perspective."},{"time":93994,"text":"Nothing really communicates \nthis scale, for example,"},{"time":97483,"text":"in context, in a way that this does."},{"time":100507,"text":"But there are a few hurdles, \nand they are quite basic"},{"time":102925,"text":"and quite fundamental."}]},{"cues":[{"time":104962,"text":"One is piloting."},{"time":106211,"text":"So for this image, they flew a camera,"},{"time":110136,"text":"a five kilogram device with an SLR under it."},{"time":114962,"text":"It's quite heavy, lots of \nspinning, sharp things."},{"time":119438,"text":"It's a bit uncomfortable to fly,"},{"time":121868,"text":"probably also for the operator."},{"time":123345,"text":"In fact, you can see that on the \nback of the pilot's shirt, it says,"},{"time":126907,"text":"\"No questions until landing\""},{"time":128966,"text":"in Russian and in English,"},{"time":130850,"text":"because people are curious, and they'll go tap you,"},{"time":133224,"text":"and then you lose your focus and things happen."},{"time":135732,"text":"And these guys are great. They're professionals;"},{"time":137947,"text":"they're really careful in what they do."},{"time":140940,"text":"So in the protests, maybe you noticed,"},{"time":143549,"text":"they flew over the river so it was quite safe."},{"time":146407,"text":"But this doesn't necessarily apply to"},{"time":149411,"text":"all people and all conditions,"},{"time":151120,"text":"so we really have to make piloting easier."}]},{"cues":[{"time":153517,"text":"The other problem is regulations,"},{"time":155799,"text":"or rather, the lack of good regulation."},{"time":158825,"text":"For many good reasons, it's just difficult"},{"time":160738,"text":"to come up with common sense laws"},{"time":162860,"text":"to regulate flying cameras."},{"time":164911,"text":"So we already have cameras."},{"time":167239,"text":"Everyone here, I'm sure, has a\nsmartphone with a camera, right?"},{"time":169815,"text":"There are more and more of them."},{"time":171447,"text":"You hear about people with\nGoogle Glass being attacked."},{"time":173621,"text":"You hear about, actually, a drone pilot,"},{"time":176321,"text":"a hobbyist, was attacked two weeks ago"},{"time":178222,"text":"because he was flying near a beach."},{"time":180348,"text":"Here's some personal input I didn't expect."},{"time":182575,"text":"Just yesterday, I was attacked by a guy"},{"time":185267,"text":"who claimed that I was filming him."},{"time":187818,"text":"I was checking my email right here —"},{"time":190517,"text":"easy way to get input for your talk."},{"time":194160,"text":"But I think there are better solutions."},{"time":195939,"text":"I think we have to defuse the situation."},{"time":197908,"text":"We have to come up with responsible solutions"},{"time":201249,"text":"that address the privacy issues"},{"time":202926,"text":"and the safety, accountability issues"},{"time":205726,"text":"but still give us that perspective."}]},{"cues":[{"time":209539,"text":"And this is one potential solution."},{"time":212722,"text":"So this is the Fotokite."},{"time":215643,"text":"Well, let me see, it's a quadrocopter,"},{"time":217526,"text":"but what's kind of special \nabout it is there's a leash."},{"time":221834,"text":"It's literally a dog leash. It's very convenient."},{"time":224928,"text":"And the neat thing about it is,"},{"time":227155,"text":"to fly it, there's no joysticks, nothing like this."},{"time":229539,"text":"You just turn it on"},{"time":231877,"text":"and you point in the direction that you want to fly."},{"time":234511,"text":"You give it a little twist."},{"time":235850,"text":"That's kind of the way you communicate."},{"time":241787,"text":"And there it goes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":243969,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":253396,"text":"So the interaction is super simple."},{"time":255377,"text":"It's like a personal flying pet."},{"time":257333,"text":"It just always maintains a certain angle to you,"},{"time":259594,"text":"and if I move around with it,"},{"time":261670,"text":"it'll actually follow me naturally."},{"time":264316,"text":"And of course, we can build on top of this."},{"time":266455,"text":"So this leash has some additional electronics."},{"time":269025,"text":"You can turn it on."},{"time":270859,"text":"And now, it's like telling your dog to fly lower,"},{"time":276080,"text":"if you have such a dog. So, I can press a button"},{"time":278638,"text":"and manipulate it rather easily."},{"time":281281,"text":"So I just shifted its position."}]},{"cues":[{"time":283970,"text":"And it's really safe."},{"time":285747,"text":"I don't know about you guys in the front row —"},{"time":288430,"text":"(Laughter) — but at least in principle,"},{"time":290674,"text":"you have to agree that you feel safer"},{"time":292789,"text":"because there is a physical connection."},{"time":294837,"text":"Live demos are hard, right?"},{"time":296355,"text":"Things go wrong all the time."},{"time":297907,"text":"But no matter what,"},{"time":299347,"text":"this thing will actually prevent this thing"},{"time":301216,"text":"from going into you."},{"time":302882,"text":"What's more, it tells you immediately that"},{"time":304970,"text":"I am the one responsible for this device."},{"time":306998,"text":"You don't have to look for someone controlling it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":309518,"text":"Now, I can tell you that it's easy a lot,"},{"time":312285,"text":"but I think a really good way to prove that"},{"time":315300,"text":"is to grab a second one"},{"time":318359,"text":"and launch it."},{"time":322364,"text":"And if I can do this on stage live,"},{"time":325647,"text":"then I can show each and every one of you"},{"time":327910,"text":"in five minutes how to \noperate one of these devices."}]},{"cues":[{"time":340659,"text":"So now we have two eyes in the sky. (Applause)"},{"time":342666,"text":"And now the trick is getting them back."},{"time":347746,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":351841,"text":"So my question now to you is,"},{"time":354255,"text":"well, it's a nice solution,"},{"time":356000,"text":"it's very accessible, it's safe."},{"time":358130,"text":"What would you use it for?"},{"time":359671,"text":"What would you use such a camera for in your life?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":363420,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":365734,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}